"title": "5870: greed, condemnation of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5870",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Greed is condemned by Scripture as contrary to the purposes of God.</p>\n<h2>Greed is a feature of the fallen world</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:3\">PSA 10:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:29\">ROM 1:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:10\">1CO 5:10</a></p>\n<h2>Greed is an expression of sinful human nature</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:21-Mark7:22\">MRK 7:21–7:22</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:19-Matt15:20\">MAT 15:19–15:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:31\">EZK 33:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:8\">ROM 7:8</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of greed</h2>\n<h3>Of individuals</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:21\">JOS 7:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:12\">EZK 22:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:23\">DAN 5:23</a></p>\n<h3>Of false teachers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:25\">MAT 23:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:13\">JER 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:10\">JER 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:39\">LUK 11:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:3\">2PE 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:14\">2PE 2:14</a></p>\n<h2>Greed invites God's judgment both now and later</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:5\">EPH 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:27\">PRO 15:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:8\">PRO 28:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:25\">PRO 28:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:4\">PRO 29:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:10-Ezek18:13\">EZK 18:10–18:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:5-Ezek28:7\">EZK 28:5–28:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:4-Amos8:7\">AMO 8:4–8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:1-Mic2:3\">MIC 2:1–2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:5-Hab2:6\">HAB 2:5–2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9-1Cor6:10\">1CO 6:9–6:10</a></p>",
